{
  "video_id": "hLltkC-G5dY",
  "title": "The playful wonderland behind great inventions | Steven Johnson",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12801.0,
      "end_time": 16696.0,
      "text": "(Music)"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 16720.0,
      "end_time": 19416.0,
      "text": "Roughly 43,000 years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19440.0,
      "end_time": 22416.0,
      "text": "a young cave bear died in the rolling hills"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22440.0,
      "end_time": 25816.0,
      "text": "on the northwest border of modern day Slovenia."
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25840.0,
      "end_time": 29936.0,
      "text": "A thousand years later, a mammoth died in southern Germany."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 29960.0,
      "end_time": 33256.0,
      "text": "A few centuries after that, a griffon vulture also died"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 33280.0,
      "end_time": 34480.0,
      "text": "in the same vicinity."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35280.0,
      "end_time": 39416.0,
      "text": "And we know almost nothing about how these animals met their deaths,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 39440.0,
      "end_time": 43495.0,
      "text": "but these different creatures dispersed across both time and space"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 43520.0,
      "end_time": 46696.0,
      "text": "did share one remarkable fate."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 46720.0,
      "end_time": 50176.0,
      "text": "After their deaths, a bone from each of their skeletons"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 50200.0,
      "end_time": 52896.0,
      "text": "was crafted by human hands"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 52920.0,
      "end_time": 54120.0,
      "text": "into a flute."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 54920.0,
      "end_time": 56376.0,
      "text": "Think about that for a second."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 56400.0,
      "end_time": 59560.0,
      "text": "Imagine you're a caveman, 40,000 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 59800.0,
      "end_time": 60736.0,
      "text": "You've mastered fire."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 60760.0,
      "end_time": 62815.0,
      "text": "You've built simple tools for hunting."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 62840.0,
      "end_time": 65456.0,
      "text": "You've learned how to craft garments from animal skins"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 65480.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67536.0,
      "text": "to keep yourself warm in the winter."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 67560.0,
      "end_time": 70296.0,
      "text": "What would you choose to invent next?"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70320.0,
      "end_time": 73455.0,
      "text": "It seems preposterous that you would invent the flute,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 73480.0,
      "end_time": 77296.0,
      "text": "a tool that created useless vibrations in air molecules."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 77319.0,
      "end_time": 80320.0,
      "text": "But that is exactly what our ancestors did."
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 81200.0,
      "end_time": 84616.0,
      "text": "Now this turns out to be surprisingly common"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 84640.0,
      "end_time": 86256.0,
      "text": "in the history of innovation."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 86280.0,
      "end_time": 88216.0,
      "text": "Sometimes people invent things"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 88240.0,
      "end_time": 91175.0,
      "text": "because they want to stay alive or feed their children"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 91200.0,
      "end_time": 93336.0,
      "text": "or conquer the village next door."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 93360.0,
      "end_time": 94776.0,
      "text": "But just as often,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 94800.0,
      "end_time": 96696.0,
      "text": "new ideas come into the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 96720.0,
      "end_time": 98760.0,
      "text": "simply because they're fun."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 99520.0,
      "end_time": 101936.0,
      "text": "And here's the really strange thing:"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 101960.0,
      "end_time": 105216.0,
      "text": "many of those playful but seemingly frivolous inventions"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 105240.0,
      "end_time": 107856.0,
      "text": "ended up sparking momentous transformations"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 107880.0,
      "end_time": 110976.0,
      "text": "in science, in politics and society."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 111000.0,
      "end_time": 114936.0,
      "text": "Take what may be the most important invention of modern times:"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 114960.0,
      "end_time": 116696.0,
      "text": "programmable computers."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 116720.0,
      "end_time": 121336.0,
      "text": "Now, the standard story is that computers descend from military technology,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 121360.0,
      "end_time": 124216.0,
      "text": "since many of the early computers were designed specifically"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 124240.0,
      "end_time": 127696.0,
      "text": "to crack wartime codes or calculate rocket trajectories."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 127720.0,
      "end_time": 131216.0,
      "text": "But in fact, the origins of the modern computer"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 131240.0,
      "end_time": 132896.0,
      "text": "are much more playful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 132920.0,
      "end_time": 134215.0,
      "text": "even musical,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 134240.0,
      "end_time": 135496.0,
      "text": "than you might imagine."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 135520.0,
      "end_time": 136776.0,
      "text": "The idea behind the flute,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 136800.0,
      "end_time": 139896.0,
      "text": "of just pushing air through tubes to make a sound,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 139920.0,
      "end_time": 142815.0,
      "text": "was eventually modified to create the first organ"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 142840.0,
      "end_time": 144576.0,
      "text": "more than 2,000 years ago."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 144600.0,
      "end_time": 147896.0,
      "text": "Someone came up with the brilliant idea of triggering sounds"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 147920.0,
      "end_time": 150815.0,
      "text": "by pressing small levers with our fingers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 150840.0,
      "end_time": 153216.0,
      "text": "inventing the first musical keyboard."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 153240.0,
      "end_time": 157376.0,
      "text": "Now, keyboards evolved from organs to clavichords to harpsichords"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 157400.0,
      "end_time": 158736.0,
      "text": "to the piano,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 158760.0,
      "end_time": 161416.0,
      "text": "until the middle of the 19th century,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 161440.0,
      "end_time": 164216.0,
      "text": "when a bunch of inventors finally hit on the idea"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 164240.0,
      "end_time": 168136.0,
      "text": "of using a keyboard to trigger not sounds but letters."
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 168160.0,
      "end_time": 170456.0,
      "text": "In fact, the very first typewriter"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 170480.0,
      "end_time": 173640.0,
      "text": "was originally called \"the writing harpsichord.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 175440.0,
      "end_time": 179256.0,
      "text": "Flutes and music led to even more powerful breakthroughs."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 179280.0,
      "end_time": 181160.0,
      "text": "About a thousand years ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 181400.0,
      "end_time": 183256.0,
      "text": "at the height of the Islamic Renaissance,"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 183280.0,
      "end_time": 185616.0,
      "text": "three brothers in Baghdad designed a device"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 185640.0,
      "end_time": 188136.0,
      "text": "that was an automated organ."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 188160.0,
      "end_time": 191400.0,
      "text": "They called it \"the instrument that plays itself.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 191960.0,
      "end_time": 195960.0,
      "text": "Now, the instrument was basically a giant music box."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 195120.0,
      "end_time": 199456.0,
      "text": "The organ could be trained to play various songs by using instructions"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 199480.0,
      "end_time": 202679.0,
      "text": "encoded by placing pins on a rotating cylinder."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 203440.0,
      "end_time": 206560.0,
      "text": "And if you wanted the machine to play a different song,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 206800.0,
      "end_time": 209400.0,
      "text": "you just swapped a new cylinder in with a different code on it."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 209840.0,
      "end_time": 213216.0,
      "text": "This instrument was the first of its kind."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 213240.0,
      "end_time": 214976.0,
      "text": "It was programmable."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 215000.0,
      "end_time": 218560.0,
      "text": "Now, conceptually, this was a massive leap forward."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 218800.0,
      "end_time": 221496.0,
      "text": "The whole idea of hardware and software"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 221520.0,
      "end_time": 224736.0,
      "text": "becomes thinkable for the first time with this invention."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 224760.0,
      "end_time": 227215.0,
      "text": "And that incredibly powerful concept"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 227240.0,
      "end_time": 230416.0,
      "text": "didn't come to us as an instrument of war or of conquest,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 230440.0,
      "end_time": 232136.0,
      "text": "or necessity at all."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 232160.0,
      "end_time": 237296.0,
      "text": "It came from the strange delight of watching a machine play music."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 237320.0,
      "end_time": 240536.0,
      "text": "In fact, the idea of programmable machines"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 240560.0,
      "end_time": 245216.0,
      "text": "was exclusively kept alive by music for about 700 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 245240.0,
      "end_time": 247736.0,
      "text": "In the 1700s, music-making machines"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 247760.0,
      "end_time": 251335.0,
      "text": "became the playthings of the Parisian elite."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 251360.0,
      "end_time": 254536.0,
      "text": "Showmen used the same coded cylinders"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 254560.0,
      "end_time": 258495.0,
      "text": "to control the physical movements of what were called automata,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 258519.0,
      "end_time": 260536.0,
      "text": "an early kind of robot."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 260560.0,
      "end_time": 262496.0,
      "text": "One of the most famous of those robots"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 262520.0,
      "end_time": 265895.0,
      "text": "was, you guessed it, an automated flute player"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 265920.0,
      "end_time": 267816.0,
      "text": "designed by a brilliant French inventor"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 267840.0,
      "end_time": 269125.0,
      "text": "named Jacques de Vaucanson."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 270279.0,
      "end_time": 273776.0,
      "text": "And as de Vaucanson was designing his robot musician,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 273800.0,
      "end_time": 275736.0,
      "text": "he had another idea."
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 275760.0,
      "end_time": 279736.0,
      "text": "If you could program a machine to make pleasing sounds,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 279760.0,
      "end_time": 284400.0,
      "text": "why not program it to weave delightful patterns of color out of cloth?"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 284920.0,
      "end_time": 289176.0,
      "text": "Instead of using the pins of the cylinder to represent musical notes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 289200.0,
      "end_time": 292296.0,
      "text": "they would represent threads with different colors."
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 292320.0,
      "end_time": 294816.0,
      "text": "If you wanted a new pattern for your fabric,"
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 294840.0,
      "end_time": 296520.0,
      "text": "you just programmed a new cylinder."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 297200.0,
      "end_time": 299840.0,
      "text": "This was the first programmable loom."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 300560.0,
      "end_time": 304736.0,
      "text": "Now, the cylinders were too expensive and time-consuming to make,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 304760.0,
      "end_time": 306296.0,
      "text": "but a half century later,"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 306320.0,
      "end_time": 308936.0,
      "text": "another French inventor named Jacquard"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 308960.0,
      "end_time": 313656.0,
      "text": "hit upon the brilliant idea of using paper-punched cards"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 313680.0,
      "end_time": 315456.0,
      "text": "instead of metal cylinders."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 315480.0,
      "end_time": 318536.0,
      "text": "Paper turned out to be much cheaper and more flexible"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 318560.0,
      "end_time": 320696.0,
      "text": "as a way of programming the device."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 320720.0,
      "end_time": 325176.0,
      "text": "That punch card system inspired Victorian inventor Charles Babbage"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 325200.0,
      "end_time": 327695.0,
      "text": "to create his analytical engine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 327720.0,
      "end_time": 330336.0,
      "text": "the first true programmable computer"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 330360.0,
      "end_time": 331696.0,
      "text": "ever designed."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 331720.0,
      "end_time": 334416.0,
      "text": "And punch cards were used by computer programmers"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 334440.0,
      "end_time": 336520.0,
      "text": "as late as the 1970s."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 337160.0,
      "end_time": 339776.0,
      "text": "So ask yourself this question:"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 339800.0,
      "end_time": 343296.0,
      "text": "what really made the modern computer possible?"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 343320.0,
      "end_time": 347336.0,
      "text": "Yes, the military involvement is an important part of the story,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 347360.0,
      "end_time": 351960.0,
      "text": "but inventing a computer also required other building blocks:"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 351120.0,
      "end_time": 352336.0,
      "text": "music boxes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 352360.0,
      "end_time": 354376.0,
      "text": "toy robot flute players,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 354400.0,
      "end_time": 355895.0,
      "text": "harpsichord keyboards,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 355920.0,
      "end_time": 358496.0,
      "text": "colorful patterns woven into fabric,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 358520.0,
      "end_time": 361335.0,
      "text": "and that's just a small part of the story."
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 361360.0,
      "end_time": 364336.0,
      "text": "There's a long list of world-changing ideas and technologies"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 364360.0,
      "end_time": 366560.0,
      "text": "that came out of play:"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 366800.0,
      "end_time": 368560.0,
      "text": "public museums, rubber,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 368800.0,
      "end_time": 370416.0,
      "text": "probability theory, the insurance business"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 370440.0,
      "end_time": 371656.0,
      "text": "and many more."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 371680.0,
      "end_time": 374400.0,
      "text": "Necessity isn't always the mother of invention."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 375800.0,
      "end_time": 379256.0,
      "text": "The playful state of mind is fundamentally exploratory,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 379280.0,
      "end_time": 382239.0,
      "text": "seeking out new possibilities in the world around us."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 382920.0,
      "end_time": 386416.0,
      "text": "And that seeking is why so many experiences"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 386440.0,
      "end_time": 389456.0,
      "text": "that started with simple delight and amusement"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 389480.0,
      "end_time": 392240.0,
      "text": "eventually led us to profound breakthroughs."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 393400.0,
      "end_time": 397256.0,
      "text": "Now, I think this has implications for how we teach kids in school"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 397280.0,
      "end_time": 399640.0,
      "text": "and how we encourage innovation in our workspaces,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 400520.0,
      "end_time": 403575.0,
      "text": "but thinking about play and delight this way"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 403600.0,
      "end_time": 407136.0,
      "text": "also helps us detect what's coming next."
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 407160.0,
      "end_time": 409536.0,
      "text": "Think about it: if you were sitting there in 1750"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 409560.0,
      "end_time": 413960.0,
      "text": "trying to figure out the big changes coming to society"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 413120.0,
      "end_time": 415160.0,
